'''Antonio Pero<U+0161>evi<U+0107>''' (born 6 March 1992 in [[Osijek]]) is a [[Croats|Croatian]] football [[midfielder]], currently playing for [[NK Osijek|Osijek]] in the [[Prva HNL]].

==Club career==
Pero<U+0161>evi<U+0107> started his career playing at youth level for his hometown club [[NK Osijek|Osijek]] with whom he had signed a scholarship contract in February 2010.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.glas-slavonije.hr/vijest.asp?rub=6&ID_VIJESTI=120750 |title=Antonio Pero<U+0161>evi<U+0107> postao alternacija za lijevi bok |last=Keler |first=Dalibor |date=19 February 2010 |work=Glas Slavonije |language=Croatian |accessdate=7 April 2012}}</ref> He made his debut for the first team as a late substitute in a 2<U+2013>0 win against [[HNK Cibalia|Cibalia]] on 13 May 2010 in the last round of [[2009<U+2013>10 Prva HNL|2009<U+2013>10 season]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hrsport.net/vijesti/397117/nogomet-1-hnl/osijek-susjedu-uskratio-drugo-mjesto |title=Osijek susjedu uskratio drugo mjesto |last=Kubatka |first=<U+017D>eljko |date=13 May 2010 |work=Sportnet.hr |language=Croatian |accessdate=7 April 2012}}</ref> After injuries kept him out of action for a year, he returned for the second part of the [[2011<U+2013>12 NK Osijek season|2011<U+2013>12 season]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.glas-slavonije.hr/vijest.asp?rub=6&ID_VIJESTI=142448 |title=Vlado Bili<U+0107> okuplja poznata lica |last=Keler |first=Dalibor |date=14 June 2011 |work=Glas Slavonije |language=Croatian |accessdate=7 April 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.glas-slavonije.hr/vijest.asp?rub=6&ID_VIJESTI=157326 |title=Pero<U+0161>evi<U+0107> protiv Splita od prve minute |last=Keler |first=Dalibor |date=23 February 2012 |work=Glas Slavonije |language=Croatian |accessdate=7 April 2012}}</ref> He scored his first goal in Prva HNL in a 2<U+2013>1 defeat against Cibalia on 11 March 2012, converting a first-half penalty.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hrsport.net/vijesti/436223/nogomet-1-hnl/cibalia-prohujala-osijekom |title=Cibalia prohujala Osijekom |last=<U+017D>bulj |first=Damir |date=11 March 2012 |work=Sportnet.hr |language=Croatian |accessdate=7 April 2012}}</ref>

